name: Degenerator Parkour
description:
Degenerator Parkour

Parkour game connecting multiple movie worlds

Tron : Legacy

Blade Runner 2049

Westworld

Enders Game

INSTRUCTION:

Press W or ↑ to move forward    +   R to run

Press S or ↓ to move backward   +   R to run

Press A or ← to move left       +   R to run

Press D or → to move right      +   R to run

Press Spacebar to jump

Click the left mouse button to shoot.

Thank you very much for your material and spiritual encouragement.

Welcome comments.
